description:
In 1985, TSA was signed a deal with Mausoleum Records label. In March-April this yaar they started recording session of English version &quot;Heavy Metal World&quot; album. This version contains selected songs from two previous albums: &quot;Live&quot; and &quot;Heavy Metal World&quot; (Polish version), in new arrangenments. Mausoleum Records released this album to Western Europe markets in August 1985, and the band went on promotion tour, plays a gigs in West Berlin, Netherlands and Belgium, with very good appeal of audience.
Some parts of this tour was recorded, and Shockwave International label performed a few promo-clips from this materials. This two track was recorded (probably) at concert in West Berlin.

